Heads-up on the "run CI" part: both repos only trigger their workflows on PRs and pushes to main — a push to a release/* branch runs nothing. So no CI fired. That
said, the local R CMD check --as-cran I already ran on both is more thorough than the CI verify gate (it includes the full build, vignettes, PDF manual, and
donttest examples), so correctness is covered regardless.

